00:26:58.560 --> 00:27:00.380
But I want to
mention what it is.

00:27:00.380 --> 00:27:02.760
The Enigma has a
theoretical maximum number

00:27:02.760 --> 00:27:06.690
of settings of 3
times 10 to the 114th.

00:27:06.690 --> 00:27:07.740
The math is at the back.

00:27:07.740 --> 00:27:08.620
You can read it.

00:27:08.620 --> 00:27:10.300
But that's far more
