01:12:07.550 --> 01:12:10.120
It went through the
war and afterwards.

01:12:10.120 --> 01:12:13.420
And it still looks in
relatively good condition.

01:12:13.420 --> 01:12:17.050
I think that these were pretty
well babied by their operators.

01:12:17.050 --> 01:12:19.040
I think they understood
the value of it.

01:12:19.040 --> 01:12:22.975
They knew that they were to
value this with their life,

01:12:22.975 --> 01:12:26.120
that if an enemy came along,
they were to destroy it.

01:12:26.120 --> 01:12:29.550
And therefore, they took
very good care of them.

01:12:29.550 --> 01:12:31.100
Although, on the
outside the box,

01:12:31.100 --> 01:12:36.870
you can see that there
is quite a bit of-- I've

01:12:36.870 --> 01:12:39.190
got something blocking it here.

01:12:39.190 --> 01:12:41.420
There's some scratches
